    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so unfair. like i'm stuck in this loop of suffering for no reason. sometimes i look at it and it feels like the only \"kind\" thing would be if it just stopped. all of it. if i could just find a way to be still and not feel anything ever again. does that sound crazy?",
